column5: I am looking at a late July trip. For those who have fished both lakes, how do they compare? I have only fished Lac Seul and Minaki. Love Lac Seul but looking for a smaller lake.
[font color=green size=3][b]Generally speaking I'd send a newbie to Lac Suel in that timeframe. Wish'in I was fish'in on Wabby
